        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer973603876" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5484564441069444305"><br/>Probably the best book I’ve read yet on the history of a particular substance. Thoroughly researched and referenced, the book provides a comprehensive overview of the history of chocolate. In addition, the authors correct misconceptions and myths, and coming from authors with a speciality on ancient Mesoamerica, they are able to go into extensive detail about the pre-Columbian uses of chocolate which most other books on the subject simply skim over. Easy read, nice flowing style too.<br/><br/><b>7 out of 10</b></span>

          </span>
