    <a title="Kevin Sedota" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5009356-kevin-sedota"><img alt="Kevin Sedota" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_50x66-82093808bca726cb3249a493fbd3bd0f.png" /></a>

